WEBVTT

00:01:59.272 --> 00:02:01.441
katika mrudio wa mawimbu mahususi

00:02:01.465 --> 00:02:04.004
hadi kilomita 30 kwa saa.

00:02:05.798 --> 00:02:07.029
Ukiachana na kasi,

00:02:07.053 --> 00:02:10.710
sauti halisi ya gari huchukiliwa
kama ya kutosha.

00:02:12.999 --> 00:02:16.586
Sheria hizi zimetengeneza maoni tofauti

00:02:16.610 --> 00:02:20.587
kati ya wale ambao wanahitaji sauti
na wale walio na hofu ya uwepo

00:02:20.611 --> 00:02:22.284
wa kelele nyingi katika jiji.

00:02:23.739 --> 00:02:28.429
Hata hivyo, Sioni kwamba
ni kelele ya gari.

00:02:29.792 --> 00:02:33.040
Naona kwamba ni sauti ya gari.